=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex66 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark gritty sound, with noise oscillator character around 650 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and impulsive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: impulsive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 649.8128
  harmonic_decay_rate: -1.9162
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8259
  pitch_clarity: 16.0770
  inharmonicity: 0.1368
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -5.1526
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 66
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 66 ---
(
{
    var trig;
    trig = Dust.ar(2);
    [(Trig1.ar(trig, 0.05) * FSinOsc.ar(600, 0, 0.2)),
    (Trig1.ar(TDelay.ar(trig, 0.1), 0.05) * FSinOsc.ar(800, 0, 0.2))]
}.play;
)
